<p>Like all our working groups, the Pubs WG needs pitch-in from members: writing on subjects close to our socialist hearts (including what your WG/caucus/campaign has been doing or plans to do); editing, design, creating ‚Äòzines and one-off flyers for our work, and doing website work to keep our MDC DSA profile dynamic. So <a href="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLScONi3oG9Na-aryyNamf4LKT2narCC84Lee8QVowGduYP3iIg/viewform">fill out our contributor‚Äôs form</a> and we‚Äôll be in touch. We need your help to spread socialist ideas and news about the chapter‚Äôs work.
